hi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/K%C3%BD-t%E1%BA%A3-t%E1%BB%89nh-%C4%90%E1%BB%97-th%E1%BA%ADp-di/poem-nSAr8ZcP2NbraWGOWyp6JA">Ký tả tỉnh Đỗ thập di - 寄左省杜拾遺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Mai/L%C5%A9ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%C3%A1c/poem-M0ri-coWzBHSCqj_dSpzXw">Lũng thượng tác - 隴上作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Mai/author-0wWyWXBTsjFesQNO4r2tUQ">Viên Mai</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-%C4%90%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-huy%E1%BB%87n-Ng%C3%B4-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-tr%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-b69cDggbtgVsdx4YW4pmOA">Lưỡng Đương huyện Ngô thập thị ngự giang thượng trạch - 兩當縣吳十侍禦江上宅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%B1-Kh%C3%A1nh/Th%E1%BB%89nh-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF-ph%E1%BA%A3n-gi%C3%A1-kinh-s%C6%B0/poem-ljWYlNa1by48BdM-GbgSbQ">Thỉnh đế phản giá kinh sư - 請帝返駕京師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%B1-Kh%C3%A1nh/author-vn-49B8xHWgiPat6tqvDUw">Trần Tự Khánh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-fZekov0n38p16zJzIaCBWA">Thu dạ hoài ngâm - 秋夜懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
